shows.title: #SCREAMERS
shows.overview: As a pair of internet experts dive into a series of frightening videos, they slowly realize that the evil behind the viral sensations is very real.

shows.title: Kudrat
shows.overview: Kudrat is a 1981 romantic drama movie starring Rajesh Khanna, Hema Malini, Vinod Khanna, and Raaj Kumar. During her visit to Shimla, Chandramukhi meets Mohan and starts remembering incidents from her past life. She soon uncovers the mystery of her previous life and attempts to bring the culprit to justice.

In the winter of 2004, a group of friends fall victim to tragic events after dialing *69 in response to a crank call.  After uncovering that these events are somehow linked to their past, they embark on a terrifying journey in hopes of ending the nightmare.

shows.title: ...And Here No Devil Can Hurt You
shows.overview: In this modern love story with classic horror vibe, an adulterous couple are having an affair in a bombed out brownstone apartment, when they realize they might not be alone.
shows.originalTitle: ...And Here No Devil Can Hurt You

shows.title: 1 Dead man, 6 Suspects, $65 Million
shows.overview: The potential suspect list in the murder of a rich mogul ranges from the family’s butler to a wide range of greedy associates who all want a payday.

shows.title: 1 Versus 100
shows.overview: After Malia's father mysteriously dies, she must confront her past and learn to live with the decisions that led to her becoming an exotic dancer.

shows.title: 10 Cloverfield Lane
shows.overview: After getting in a car accident, a young woman is held in an underground bunker by a man who insists that a widespread chemical attack has left the surface of the Earth uninhabitable.

shows.title: 10 Minutes Gone
shows.overview: Action legends Bruce Willis (Die Hard) and Michael Chiklis ("The Shield") light up this edge-of-your seat thriller. Crime boss Rex hires Frank to steal a priceless jewel stash-but the job goes wrong when someone tips off the cops. After suffering a blow to the head, Frank wakes up to find the jewels gone and no memory of his attacker. Now he must find the traitor within his team.

shows.title: 10 Year Reunion
shows.overview: During a high school reunion, the four members of an inseparable clique unearth a time capsule and learn the death of their friend wasn’t an accident.

shows.title: 10x10
shows.overview: After a man abducts a seemingly innocent flower shop owner, he holds her captive in a small room, desperately trying to get her to confess a secret.

shows.title: 100 Ghost Street: The Return of Richard Speck
shows.overview: Presents footage released from paranormal investigators documenting the last days of Richard Speck's victims and his ghost at his heinous crime scene.
shows.originalTitle: 100 Ghost Street: The Return of Richard Speck

shows.overview: Investigative journalist Gowtham's life turns into a nightmare when a recurring dream haunts his reality. To find the truth, he must make a bigger sacrifice.

shows.title: 12th Man
shows.overview: Eleven friends get together for a bachelor party, but the celebrations go awry because of a phone call and a death. A drunk cop steps in to unravel the mystery.

shows.title: 13 Ghosts
shows.overview: Inside the turn-of-the-century mansion he inherited, a paleontologist and his family find themselves plagued by the ghosts of its former owners.

shows.title: 13th Child
shows.overview: A series of vicious murders in the New Jersey Pine Barrens cause an investigator to question if the Jersey Devil, a winged beast that locals claim has haunted the Barrens for over 250 years, isn't just a myth.
A man who specialises in debunking paranormal occurrences checks into the fabled room 1408 in the Dolphin Hotel. Soon after settling in, he confronts genuine terror.

shows.title: 141 A.D. Mission in Dacia
shows.overview: When a deadly epidemic threatens to run rampant through the Roman Empire, four soldiers are sent beyond its borders in search of a rumored cure.

shows.title: 1920 London
shows.overview: Shivangi leads a peaceful life with Veer in London until Veer starts behaving strangely. Shivangi is asked to meet a powerful exorcist, Jai Singh Gujjar, who is her ex-boyfriend. Shivangi shares her ordeal with Jai who then fights the witch possessing Veer and saves his life.

shows.title: 2 Bedroom 1 Bath
shows.overview: A young couple moves into their perfect home, but when they discovered that they will soon become parents, things begin to fall apart.

shows.title: 2 Cool 2 Be 4gotten
shows.overview: Felix is a friendless achiever in high school whose life changes after the arrival of the half-American Snyder brothers, entangling him in their dark ambitions.
